<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/33985196">飞行器专业术语里的&quot;突风缓和系统&quot;指的是什么？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="5800663" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">具体包含哪些成分或者部件？有什么作用？它又是如何实现的？<br><br><img data-rawheight="1080" data-rawwidth="1440" src="//pic1.zhimg.com/d9ae78583be9875f626765b85e4ec8dc_b.png" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/d9ae78583be9875f626765b85e4ec8dc_r.png"></div>


</div>
