<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="183">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$nai-he-jiu-shi-jiu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/nai-he-jiu-shi-jiu" class="zg-link" title="帝执">帝执</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$phaladius" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/phaladius" class="zg-link" title="道鱼酱">道鱼酱</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="5800663" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">题图是西工大《战斗机气动布局设计》第96页：<blockquote>鸭式飞机的低空驾驭性较好, 因为,鸭式飞机一般采用大后掠小展弦比机翼 , 它的升力线斜率较低,鸭翼位置靠近驾驶员, 有利于突风缓和系统的应用。 <br></blockquote><br><br>“突风”，或者叫“阵风”，就是竖直方向上突然来的一阵风，二次元也叫“<a href="http://zh.moegirl.org/zh/%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E6%B0%94%E6%B5%81" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">上升气流 - 萌娘百科<i class="icon-external"></i></a>”。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/0c2909124da1b5fba86cdca9a244f8c9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="576" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/0c2909124da1b5fba86cdca9a244f8c9_r.jpg">图1：喜闻乐见的上升气流</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="576" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1024" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/0c2909124da1b5fba86cdca9a244f8c9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/0c2909124da1b5fba86cdca9a244f8c9_b.jpg">图1：喜闻乐见的上升气流<br><br><br>突风会改变飞行器的相对迎角，从而改变升力的大小，产生不平衡，所以需要缓和。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/db3a3f3af4a1430b1849e80be0f2ee1c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="379" data-rawheight="227" class="content_image" width="379">图2：阵风对迎角的影响</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="379" data-rawheight="227" class="content_image lazy" width="379" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/db3a3f3af4a1430b1849e80be0f2ee1c_b.jpg">图2：阵风对迎角的影响<br><br><br>比如飞机迎面来了一阵上升气流，导致了额外的升力，此时飞机需要调整舵面来抵消不速之力。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/e30d91bff2bcd5cb950197c9f9e6ee68_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="820" data-rawheight="672" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="820" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/e30d91bff2bcd5cb950197c9f9e6ee68_r.jpg">图3：突风对升力的影响与抑制</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="820" data-rawheight="672" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="820" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/e30d91bff2bcd5cb950197c9f9e6ee68_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/e30d91bff2bcd5cb950197c9f9e6ee68_b.jpg">图3：突风对升力的影响与抑制<br><br><br>这个调整的依据是加速度计的数据，然后再经过卡曼滤波处理。整个系统分为计算模块和控制模块两部分。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/328fb035f91af8b9b7d31a0a0fe8499d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="362" data-rawheight="301" class="content_image" width="362"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="362" data-rawheight="301" class="content_image lazy" width="362" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/328fb035f91af8b9b7d31a0a0fe8499d_b.jpg"><br>图4：突风缓和系统<br><br><br>再回到题图的这段话上来，他实际上说了三件事：<br><ol><li>“鸭式飞机的低空驾驭性较好”——因为对流层的突风更频繁，所以才会说到突风缓和；</li><li>“升力线斜率较低”——升力对突风不敏感，降低了操作的难度；<br></li><li>“鸭翼位置靠近驾驶员”——鸭翼离重心远，产生的力矩大，容易实现配平。</li></ol>


</div>

</div>
